metadata.name: MetaApe
metadata.description:
MetaApe

The Inspiration of Meta Ape comes from the trend of "Ape follow Ape" by the community of BAYC. 

There's a lot of Ape related NFT projects that manage to bring everyone together by the spirit of "Apes Together Strong". 
 
There's a tons of small details and textures that related to crypto, NFT, smart contract, fiat and so on being use to enhance the visual message on this piece of art.


Dimension: 6000px x 7500px
